HEADWORD: Tuberose
<hw>Tube"rose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G.
<ets>tuberose</ets>, F. <ets>tub⟦eacute⟧reuse</ets>, NL. <ets>Polianthes
